  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction à fdk-aac</title>

    <para>
      <application>fdk-aac</application> package provides the Fraunhofer FDK AAC
      library, which is purported to be a high quality Advanced Audio Coding
      implementation.
    </para>

    &lfs74_checked;

